casebody.data:
Ricky TURNER
v.
CHERRY HOSPITAL No. 403P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 31, 2016 Ricky Turner, for Turner, Ricky.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 26th of October 2016 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wayne County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 31st of October 2016."
